364778","time":"2018-7-10 13:18","userId":"401575","userName":"BINDERY","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">kylecalloway⭐SVIP3⭐</span> 说: 要传网盘只能加密压缩，并且不要在网盘内解压（百毒会记录密码并分析你的文件）</q></div>那onedrive呢？"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/40/15/401575.jpg","floor":"#5-2","id":"1364784","time":"2018-7-10 13:28","userId":"401575","userName":"BINDERY","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">kylecalloway⭐SVIP3⭐</span> 说: 网盘默认指百毒吧。国外的网盘免费容量都挺小的，一般备份文档用。应该不会像国内一样流氓</q></div>用的是onedrive for business，空间是够了但是还是不太放心"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/40/15/401575.jpg","floor":"#5-3","id":"1364806","time":"2018-7-10 14:21","userId":"401575","userName":"BINDERY","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">kylecalloway⭐SVIP3⭐</span> 说: 我觉得只要不是ETSQ，应该都不会和谐。<br>稍微搜了一下，如果违规貌似会先提醒的<br><br>而且你可以换号问问客服呀</q></div>好的，谢谢大佬！"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/02/35/23570.jpg","floor":"#6","id":"1364775","time":"2018-7-10 13:15","userId":"htsune_miku","userName":"Jadeity","userSign":"(明天，我就要去屠龙（失恋了，不想再屠龙了） ...)","message":"为何麻烦？我觉得要备份的话打包一下更好啊。","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/40/15/401575.jpg","floor":"#6-1","id":"1364777","time":"2018-7-10 13:17","userId":"401575","userName":"BINDERY","userSign":"","message":"但是几百G的文件打包和解压都要好久啊"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/02/35/23570.jpg","floor":"#6-2","id":"1364786","time":"2018-7-10 13:32","userId":"htsune_miku","userName":"Jadeity","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">BINDERY</span> 说: 但是几百G的文件打包和解压都要好久啊</q></div>那就直接修改二进制文件吧"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/40/15/401575.jpg","floor":"#6-3","id":"1364789","time":"2018-7-10 13:34","userId":"401575","userName":"BINDERY","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Jadeity</span> 说: 那就直接修改二进制文件吧</q></div>有什么办法批量修改吗？"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.t