iles/tv/20.gif\" smileid=\"59\" alt=\"(bgm43)\">"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/11/88/118807.jpg","floor":"#9-5","id":"1364823","time":"2018-7-10 14:57","userId":"kuri_ko","userName":"桜野くりこ","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">BINDERY</span> 说: 问题是我没有编程基础啊</q></div>批处理 给当前目录下所有文件(*.*)末尾追加一个换行：for /f \"usebackq delims=?\" %i in (`dir /b *.*`) do echo.>>\"%i\""},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/40/15/401575.jpg","floor":"#9-6","id":"1364832","time":"2018-7-10 15:36","userId":"401575","userName":"BINDERY","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">桜野くりこ.lnk</span> 说: 批处理 给当前目录下所有文件(*.*)末尾追加一个换行：for /f \"usebackq delims=?\" %i in (`dir /b *.*`) do echo.>>\"%i\"</q></div>好像用不了哦"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/22/04/220491.jpg","floor":"#9-7","id":"1364833","time":"2018-7-10 15:38","userId":"chaserhkj","userName":"Chaser","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">BINDERY</span> 说: 本来是打算学的，但是明年就要高考了呀</q></div>原来是高中生<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">（"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/11/88/118807.jpg","floor":"#9-8","id":"1364844","time":"2018-7-10 16:05","userId":"kuri_ko","userName":"桜野くりこ","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">BINDERY</span> 说: 好像用不了哦</q></div>写在批处理文件里的话要把所有%i改成%%i<br><div class=\"codeHighlight\"><pre><br>::转到批处理文件所在目录<br>pushd \"%~dp0\"<br>::循环添加换行<br>for /f \"usebackq delims=?\" %%i in (`dir /b *.*`) do echo.>>\"%%i\"<br></pre></div>"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/40/15/401575.jpg","floor":"#9-9","id":"1364846","time":"2018-7-10 16:16","userId":"401575","userName":"BINDERY","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">桜野くりこ.lnk</span> 说: 写在批处理文件里的话要把所有%i改成%%i<br><br>::转到批处理文件所在目录<br>pushd \"%~dp0\"<br>::循环添加换行<br>for /f \"usebackq delims=?\" %%i in (`dir ...</q></div>可以用了，但是子目录里面的文件要怎么办？还有要怎么恢复呢？"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/11/88/118807.jpg","floor":"#9-10","id":"1364891","time":"2018-7-10 16:58","userId":"kuri_ko","userName":"桜野くりこ","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">BINDERY</span> 说: 可以用了，但是子目录里面的文件要怎么办？还有要怎么恢复呢？</q></div>包含子目录里的把dir /b改成dir /s /b就行了<br>恢复.....可以考虑处理之前把原本的文件长度存下来：dir /s > list.txt<br>恢复的时候直接按原本的长度截取文件就行了（用批处理不好实现）"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/31/25/312525.jpg","floor":"#9-11","id":"1365023","time":"2018-7-11 10:38","userId":"312525","userName":"小仓鼠","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">BINDERY</span> 说: 本来是打算学的，但是明年就要高考了呀</q></div>怂什么，前两天我还看漫画分析黄漫画师呢"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/17/18/171851.jpg","floor":"#10","id":"1364835","time":"2018-7-10 15:42","userId":"yonjar","userName":"🍋LautlosP🍋","userSign":"(DD集まれ! (๑•̀ㅂ•́)و✧)","message":"只是备份不分享的话还怕什么被和谐<br>用的啥网盘？","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/40/15/401575.jpg","floor":"#10-1","id":"1364838","time":"2018-7-10 15:49","userId":"401575","userName":"BINDERY","userSign":"","message":"onedrive for business"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/01/00/10097.jpg","floor":"#11","id":"1364839","time":"2018-7-10 15:50","userId":"dhww","userName":"无望","userSign":"","message":"所有网盘都没物理硬盘保险。最便宜的4T硬盘才700左右，存储容量/价格比要比网盘会员高得多。而且不用担心被和谐，没有文件数量文件大小限制，数据读写比网盘上传下载方便不知道多少。","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/25/02/250298.jpg","floor":"#12","id":"1364851","time":"2018-7-10 16:35","userId":"hupanxx","userName":"Panzerance🀃","userSign":"(いいんです)","message":"OD 怕啥河蟹<br>又不是百度云<br>就是文件大小限制 15G","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/25/77/257753.jpg","floor":"#13","id":"1364908","time":"2018-7-10 18:33","userId":"257753","userName":"为了坚果","userSign":"","message":"md5不变你怎么改都能被检测出来。","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/42/01/420149.jpg","floor":"#14","id":"1364927","time":"2018-7-10 20:00","userId"